  "notes": [
    "This study demonstrates a novel CRISPR/dCas9-based approach for targeted demethylation of the BRD7 promoter as a therapeutic strategy for nasopharyngeal carcinoma",
    "The research shows that hypermethylation of the BRD7 promoter is a key mechanism for BRD7 downregulation in NPC",
    "The lentivirus-mediated delivery system shows promise for clinical translation with demonstrated safety and efficacy in xenograft models"
